          "heading": "<p>Here's why <em>Rejuvia works better</em></p>",
          "description": "<p>Rejuvia isn't a pill or a gummy. It's <strong>a sublingual spray.</strong></p><p>You spray Rejuvia under your tongue, where the tissue is packed with blood vessels. The ingredients absorb directly into your bloodstream. No stomach. No liver. No wasted ingredients.</p><p>More of the formula reaches your body. So you feel it working in minutes, not an hour from now.</p>",
