      "founder_note_v2_nAYH3a": {
        "type": "founder-note-v2",
        "disabled": true,
        "name": "Founder Note V2",
        "settings": {
          "heading": "A Note from Our Founder",
          "text": "<p>Look, I know you're skeptical. <strong>You should be.</strong> You've spent years and hundreds of dollars on products that promised to fix your sleep and didn't.</p><p>I'm not going to tell you Rejuvia is magic. It's not. It's mint-flavored spray made from 13 plants and herbs that your great-grandmother probably could have named.</p><p><strong>The only thing we did differently is put them in a format your body can actually absorb. That's it. That's the whole innovation.</strong></p><p>If it doesn't work for you, email us within 90 days and <strong>we'll refund every cent.</strong> Try one bottle. Give it a few nights. And if you don't notice a difference, it costs you nothing.</p><p><strong>That's a fair deal from a family that just wants you to sleep.</strong></p>",
          "image": "shopify://shop_images/Image_5.png",
          "signature_image": "shopify://shop_images/Frame_48101400.png",
          "signature_name": "RC Williams",
